title: RYK Vector Wave Synth Module Review
description:
The RYK Vector Wave is a powerhouse of digital synthesis in Eurorack, offering FM, Vector Synthesis, internal modulation, polyphony, and more. Oh, and it has a joystick. Let's tuck in.
